                                    Name: "no_declined_r8_trainer_dune"
                                }
                            ],
                            Label: "bow_out_button"
                        }
                    ],
                    Texts: [
                        {
                            Text: "You look like you are cutting across to Kalahar. Gaia does not go easy on soft feet. Race me across the flat first - one run, no shame in declining."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "The dunes pay in sand and lessons. Both stick in your teeth for a week. Take a run or ride on, your call."
                        },
                        {
                            Text: "Kalahar Reach and Gaia wait over the crest. A dune race now beats a surprise later - but declining is cheap enough."
                        }
                    ],
                    Name: "Duneracer Kito",
                    Label: "default"
                }
            ]
